      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You can modify a <em>serum of healing</em> to synergize with your target’s genetic code.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Life Science 5 ranks.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: With 1 minute of work, you can modify a <em>serum of healing</em> so that when it’s consumed by or administered to a specific creature, it restores a number of additional Hit Points equal to the serum’s item level. You can modify a number of serums this way each day equal to your Intelligence modifier. These modifications expire after 24 hours, returning the serum to its normal function.</p>"
